{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act40side", "eventName": "相見歡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OR-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "雪裡紅", "storyInfo": "煌來到鼎豐樓參加百珍宴的廚師選拔賽，與此同時，驚蟄也來此查案。煌歪打正著地通過了層層選拔，與莫不服會面時，鼎豐樓比賽現場卻突然起火。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎光臨鼎豐樓。", "name": "禮貌的招待"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_dailylifeofbaizao_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇……這就是傳說中的鼎豐樓。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……還緊張嗎？", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？有什麼好緊張的。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬上就要比賽了，可為什麼，我有種心虛的感覺……", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟……", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕什麼，小大廚最後都說可以了。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，我們又不是真的是去當廚師的，我們只是想找到那位傳奇大廚，親口問問他那種桔紅酥的做法。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，也只能這麼說服自己了……", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間差不多了。觀賽的客官請在這裡留步，參賽的廚師請隨我上前。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遇到難題的時候，千萬別衝動，冷靜思考，總有辦法的……", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，我去啦。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請坐。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖說您今天是來參加考試的，但遠來是客，還請先用一杯茶。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考官端起桌上的茶壺，為煌倒上茶水，清甜的香味頓時盈滿鼻腔。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說是比賽，這氛圍還蠻友好的嘛……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好路上口渴，多謝啦！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌拿起茶盞，仰頭滿飲。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，考官將紙筆放在她的面前。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這壺茶中泡了幾味料，寫下來。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "煌", "content": "噗——"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "煌", "content": "咳咳咳咳……什麼？！"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌看向自己的茶盞，僅剩的一點水珠掛在杯壁上。煌又抬起頭看向了眼前的考官，他的臉上依然掛著一副禮貌的微笑。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還能……再來一杯嗎？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g10_restaurantkitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1636_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看今天應該是沒希望啦，從上午到現在來了幾十號人，到現在這第一關都沒人能過。", "name": "悠閒的廚師"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1636_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總廚出題也太刁鑽了，考試的人一進門就是這樣一齣，換誰來都會傻掉啊。", "name": "無聊的廚師"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舌頭就是廚師的眼睛，要是舌頭上的功夫不過關，廚藝也高不到哪裡去。", "name": "悠閒的廚師"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連這一關都過不了，那也不用浪費總廚時間了，還是叫他們早些打道回府的好。", "name": "悠閒的廚師"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸客人，這裡可是廚房。你怎麼——", "name": "悠閒的廚師"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大理寺查案，煩請各位配合。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷靜……冷靜……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mechanist說過，人的舌頭只能嚐出四種味道，但是鼻子可以分辨出上百種味道……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我也沒有從他的“機油”酒中聞出過什麼味就是了……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌小心翼翼地端起已經沒那麼燙的茶盞，仔細嗅聞著杯中餘味。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能聞到花香，應該是茉莉花的味道……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不只是茉莉花，還有一種……對，是菊花！小大廚飯館裡待客的菊花茶就是這種味道！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了花香，茶水喝下去的時候，我記得明明有一點酸甜味……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面的料都不帶酸，那最後的那點味道到底是什麼……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個酸酸甜甜的味道，好像有點熟悉？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g2_downtownarea", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要帶我來喝這個梅子酒？", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這梅子酒，其實也算百灶的一樣特色。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在百灶城北方，有一大片梅林。每年六月初夏，新鮮的梅子成熟的時候，人們會採下許多拿來泡酒，最好是用小寒酒來泡。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……這種苔麥釀成的酒，有種特殊的香味，搭配梅子正好。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡製三個月左右的時間，到中秋就剛好能喝了。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅子酒……也有什麼歷史嗎？", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才不是問我……那些百灶建城時犧牲的人，後來都怎樣了嗎？", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實也算不上什麼歷史，我只是想起，在過去條件艱苦的時候，梅乾是工人們常吃的一種食物。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在百灶城建好後，不知哪一年起，城北的山上，就有了這樣一片梅林。不知是何時，也不知是誰種下的。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也算是……一種紀念？", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，他們從來沒有被忘記……", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，等明年梅子熟的時候，我可以帶你去山上看看。", "name": "行箸"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是我的答案。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉花、野菊、青梅、天岳春、冰糖……小寒酒？", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，百灶的北面有片梅林。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "六月採的梅子做酒，釀到中秋剛好。這裡用的梅子應該是早前採的，所以酸澀味還沒完全去掉。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒氣在煮茶時消散，所以只剩下梅子的酸甜口感，再加上使用的花朵本身溫和的口感和淡香……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然剛入口時並不明顯，但回味讓人印象深刻……還想再來一杯！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能嚐出前幾味材料應該是情理之中，但是能嚐出這是用了小寒酒的，你還是今天頭一個。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……說對了？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道對自己給出的答案沒有自信？", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒！沒有！當然不是……哈哈……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那恭喜你通過第一關。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請隨我上樓。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_beatgong"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen", "delay": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後堂傳來一聲擊鑼聲，煌身旁的大門緩緩打開。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一關……？還有幾關啊……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g10_restaurantkitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1636_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人……這是您要的，鼎豐樓廚師的名錄。", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能不能麻煩問問，您到底是來查什麼的……？", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大理寺重要密案，暫時不方便告知。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#3$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的總廚，名字叫莫不服？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#2$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，莫大廚的名號，整個百灶廚界誰人不知？", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知不知道，在來到鼎豐樓以前，莫不服做的是什麼工作？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這我可就不知道了……莫大廚來鼎豐樓也就不到十年的時間，說長不長說短不短，但他的廚藝確實出神入化，很快就接了老總廚的班。", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他現在在哪裡？我需要見他。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#2$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在不好意思，總廚他現在正在主持考試，實在不方便見您。", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考試？什麼考試？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您就當是鼎豐樓的招生考試？好幾年才舉辦一屆的。", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要是感興趣的話，這裡也能看到轉播哦！", "name": "鼎豐樓廚師"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這參賽的人……", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#3$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1612_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌……？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1612_1#10$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g11_yanroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_act40side_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不是酒樓嗎……為什麼這個房間好像書房？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鼎豐樓數百年歷史，接待過無數名士大家，鼎豐樓特意留了這樣一間書房，來保存他們的墨寶。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珍饈書畫，都是瑰寶，都見功夫。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌仰頭望去，房頂垂下千百根絲線，每根絲線都繫著一塊木牌，似一張帷幕。"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這上面寫的，都是菜名……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該知道，鼎豐樓如今招納廚師，是為了百珍宴做準備。這要求廚師不只有廚藝，也得瞭解自己做的菜品的意義。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掛在這裡的，都是歷屆百珍宴上有來頭的菜品。你抽一塊木牌，說出這道菜的來歷，便是今天的第二關。", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（百珍宴的菜？我哪知道？！）", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（都到這一步了——）", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodensign", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌閉上眼睛，猛地抽下一塊木牌。臨近的木牌互相牽動，發出連綿的碰撞聲。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“天下一白”？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌小姐基本沒有什麼煮飯的知識，能闖過第一關已經是僥倖。", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從小在維多利亞長大，怎麼可能知道這些故事……", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌小姐……這我可幫不了你啊……", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g11_yanroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間有限。這道菜的出處，你知道嗎？", "name": "嚴厲的考官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1635_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概五十年前，炎國的太師向真龍獻上了一道菜，是一道再簡單不過的清燉蘿蔔。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但特殊之處在於，這道菜用到的蘿蔔來自天南地北，本身的味道口感相差巨大。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是蘿蔔經過長時間燉煮，吸足了湯汁，吃到嘴裡，都是一樣好吃。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，炎國向來十分重視教育，可炎國太大，各個城市的環境也是天差地別，越是偏遠的地區，學生越難有所成。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位太師是想告訴真龍，天下學子，不論出身，都該有平等的機會。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真龍聽取了太師的建議，著力支持教育改革，努力打破了辦學講學在地域上的限制，平均分配教育資源。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二年，百灶學宮發榜，錄取的一千多人裡，偏遠地區出身的學子有一半多。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往後的幾十年裡，天師府深造的天師、學宮中寒窗苦讀的學子，都十分感謝當年太師的直言進諫……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這應該，就是這道“天下一白”的含義……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌話音剛落，她感到觀眾席的交談聲頓時小了下來。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，她的感覺並沒有錯，所有人都在盯著她，神色緊張。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（煌小姐……為什麼知道這件事？）", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#7$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這裡的出題人，怎麼還會留著這道菜……）", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那個人，可不是能當眾提起的啊……）", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g11_yanroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是說錯了什麼嗎……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有意思。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音自幾丈高之處落下，煌抬頭望去，卻不見人影。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenstairfts"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腳步踩在樓梯的木板上，發出一陣悶響，它沉穩有力，讓人無法忽略。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音越來越近，煌終於勉強能看清來者——嚴肅的長者從長階上緩緩走下。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到過了這麼多年，還有人記得這事。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#9$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您就是……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你講的這個故事，年紀可比你大，姑娘，你是怎麼知道的？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是很久以前，我的家人跟我講過的故事。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人說，他就是當年那無數寒門學子之一。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "飲水思源，想來你的家人也是一個重情重義的人。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#3$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是你……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是懷著什麼心思來到這裡的？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……當然是……準備認真參加比賽的……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經站到了這裡，那我就給你一個機會。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一關，堂堂正正地，做一道“菜”。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我來。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g1_yusrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不到飯點，飯館裡只零星坐著幾個客人，卻不見跑堂與老闆，廚房也是一片寂靜。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位兄弟！幫幫忙吧！", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天出門實在著急，忘了帶飯錢。這位兄弟一看就是大家公子，行行好，借我一點錢吧！", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不白拿你的，喏，這塊家傳寶玉先抵在你這。等我回頭拿了錢再找你贖回它。", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "借給您倒也無妨……可是您既然有這樣的麻煩，直接和這裡的老闆說明不就好了嗎……？我們素不相識，您又怎麼把錢還我？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不一樣不一樣，這塊寶玉可不是凡物，不是交到誰手裡都行的。我是見公子氣度不凡，這才委託您保管一下的。", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……好吧……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左樂從口袋裡掏出一點零錢交給食客，食客拿到了錢，立刻喜上眉梢。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您打算何時把錢還給我……？我們要約在哪裡見？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有緣則見，無緣就不見。要是無緣，公子拿這塊玉典當換錢就行。", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心放心，這筆生意，公子不會虧的。", "name": "窘迫的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音未落，食客一溜煙地跑出了飯館，消失在人群裡。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "典當……換錢？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g10_restaurantkitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我準備的菜，品相不錯吧？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……長壽麵？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫不服的手落在案上，遲遲沒有動筷。他沉默了許久，才拿起勺子，嚐了一口湯。"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌小心地觀察著莫大廚，可她期待的那種滿意的神情遲遲沒有在老人臉上出現。"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#2$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這碗麵……這個湯底，是誰教你做的？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小不點廚師教的。為了學會怎麼做可是花了我不少功夫呢……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“餘味居”的老闆，是你什麼人？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowl_smash"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……欺人太甚！", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看他有些天分，想給他一個機會大展身手。可他不領情也就罷了，現在還要派一個半吊子來羞辱我！", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g15_restaurantlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌明明很順利地完成了……味道按理說不會差才對。", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……莫不服，難道認識小大廚？", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#6$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g10_restaurantkitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等！你先等一下！ ", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起！我知道你肯定一眼就能看出我根本不會煮飯，我也不是故意來你的比賽上搗亂的！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是有個問題，我必須向你請教！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小生活在維多利亞，那時我遠在炎國的家人經常會寄一種桔紅酥給我。味道很甜，很好吃……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來百灶後找了很久，但一直沒有找到那種味道……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，你是全百灶最好的廚師，你也許會知道！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是一味點心？這個問題值得你專門參加比賽來找我？", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#1$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還有很多問題！但現在靠我一個人，只能解決這一個。這是我唯一能接觸到的與我家人有關的線索了！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……做桔紅酥最忌諱的就是一味加糖，用甜味去掩蓋手藝不精和用料不佳。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不知道誰有那麼大的本事，能把桔紅酥做得又甜又好吃。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要問的問題問完了，走吧。", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#5$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等——", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 470, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenladder"}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩人的正上方響起沉悶的聲音，煌和莫不服抬頭看去，臉龐卻被什麼東西打濕。"}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1619_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡怎麼會漏水……", "name": "莫不服"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1619_1#8$1"}, {"id": 479, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對……是油！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 481, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_kjerag_h_intro", "key": "$m_bat_kjerag_h_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic"}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 1.0, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 1.0, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，穹頂懸掛的吊燈瞬間燃起，化成一個火球——"}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快躲開！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 490, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 492, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 493, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}